# Testing & Quality — web_app

## Tools
- Unit/UI: React Testing Library + Jest
- E2E: Playwright
- Coverage: 80%+ overall, block CI on drop

## Practices
- Test only behavior and contracts, not implementation details
- Mock network via MSW; avoid shallow rendering
- Deterministic tests; seed RNG when needed

## CI
- Run lint, type-check, unit, e2e (smoke) on PR
- Upload coverage artifacts and HTML report